      "body" : "In commit \"cuckoocache: Return approximate memory size, failure\" (6d0d7d9759c90c0533528893ce084f04be9387ee)\r\n\r\nI think it is worth adding a release note in this commit documenting that `-maxsigcachesize` internal cap is removed, so existing configurations with larger values may now be broken or demand more memory.",
